{
  "text": "We have here, I believe, a very important principle with respect to the law of one. You have stated that the aptitude of the individual is of paramount importance for the Orion entity to be able to be affected. Can you please explain how the uh this mechanism works in with respect to the law of one and why the attitude of the entity is of paramount importance and why this allows for uh action by the Orion entity. Thus those whose desires are shallow or transitory experience only after configurations of what might be called the magical circumcepts. A a full chrome which swings as a mind, body, spirit complex is a will to service. If this will and desire is for service to others. The corresponding polarity will be activated in the circumstance of this group. There are three such wills acting as one with a instrument in the shall we say the central position of fidelity to service. This is as it must be for the balance of the working and the continuance of the contact our vibratory complex is one appointed in these workings, also, and our will to serve is also of some degree of purity. This has created a the attraction of the polar opposite, which you experience, we may note that such a configuration of free will one pointed in service to others also has the potential for the alerting of a great mass of light strength. This positive light strength however operates also under free will and must be in a book. Must above all things be preserved. Thus you wend your way through experiences biases which may be helpful.",
  "timestamps": {
    "segment": [
      {
        "segment": "We have here, I believe, a very important principle with respect to the law of one.",
        "start_offset": 28,
