        "end_offset": 4328,
        "start": 302.0,
        "end": 346.24
      },
      {
        "segment": "This is as it must be for the balance of the working and the continuance of the contact our vibratory complex is one appointed in these workings, also, and our will to serve is also of some degree of purity.",
        "start_offset": 4367,
        "end_offset": 5317,
        "start": 349.36,
        "end": 425.36
      },
      {
        "segment": "This has created a the attraction of the polar opposite, which you experience, we may note that such a configuration of free will one pointed in service to others also has the potential for the alerting of a great mass of light strength.",
        "start_offset": 5368,
        "end_offset": 6585,
        "start": 429.44,
        "end": 526.8
      },
      {
        "segment": "This positive light strength however operates also under free will and must be in a book.",
        "start_offset": 6607,
        "end_offset": 6979,
